        <body>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="edition">
                <ab>The present edition and translation after <bibl><ptr target="cic-bibl:ECIC-III"/>: <biblScope>473</biblScope></bibl>.</ab>
           </div>
            <div type="edition" xml:lang="x-oldcam-Latn-CI" xml:space="preserve" rend="break-physical-lines"> 
                <ab type="textpart" n="anterior face">&#160;</ab>
                <ab type="invocation">om̐</ab>
                <ab> 
                    <lb n="1"/> <pc>◦</pc> svasti <pc>◦</pc> namaś śivāya
                    <lb n="2"/> umāmaheśvarassyādisarvvasi
                    <lb break="no" n="3"/>ddhipra<unclear>d</unclear>āye mahanirvighnam astu <pc>◦</pc>
                </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <ab>
                    <app loc="3"> 
                        <lem>maha°</lem>
                        <note><foreign>mahā°</foreign> seems to be intended.</note>
                    </app>
                </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <p> <foreign>Om</foreign>. Hail! Homage to Śiva – Umāmaheśvara etc. (?) – who gives every success! May there be not (?) the slighest obstacle! </p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="fr">
                <p> <foreign>Om</foreign>. Salut ! Hommage à Śiva – Umāmaheśvara etc (?) – qui donne tout succès ! Qu'il n'y ait le moindre (?) obstacle !</p>
            </div> 
            <!-- AG add sec. bibliogr. --> <!-- AL: que voudrais-tu y mettre? -->
